---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<section id="about" class="bg-dark-light py-20">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h2 class="section-title" data-aos="fade-right">Sobre Mí</h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
      <div class="about-image" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="image-container relative w-full max-w-md mx-auto">
            <!-- Use an image from a stock service or placeholder if no actual image is available -->
            <img 
              src="/MIlogo.png" 
              alt="Ignacio Castillo" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg z-10 relative "
            />
            <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-lg"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-content" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="200">
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Desarrollador apasionado por crear experiencias nuevas dentro del mundo de las tecnologías, actualmente aprendiendo sobre la ciencia de datos y microservicios con Flask y Django API Rest.
        </p>
        
        <div class="terminal bg-dark rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-gray-700 shadow-lg">
          <div class="terminal-header bg-dark-lighter px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
            <span class="ml-4 text-sm text-gray-400">datos_personales.json</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="terminal-content p-4 font-mono text-sm">
            <div class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-400">></span> 
              <span class="text-blue-400">Nombre:</span> 
              <span class="text-white" id="name-typing">Ignacio Castillo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-400">></span> 
              <span class="text-blue-400">Rol:</span> 
              <span class="text-white" id="role-typing">Desarrollador back-end y front-end</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-400">></span> 
              <span class="text-blue-400">Estado:</span> 
              <span class="text-white" id="status-typing">aprendiendo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-400">></span> 
              <span class="text-blue-400">Ubicación:</span> 
              <span class="text-white" id="location-typing">Concepción, Chile</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-400">></span> 
              <span class="text-primary blink-cursor">_</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-purple-600">Educación</h3>
            <p>Ingeniería en Informática</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Universidad Tecnica Federico Santa Maria</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-purple-600">Experiencia</h3>
            <p>Desarrollador Django y astro</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">1 año de experiencia</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }
  
  .blink-cursor {
    animation: blink 1s infinite;
  }
  
  .terminal {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .terminal::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(20, 241, 149, 0.05) 0%, rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.05) 100%);
    z-index: -1;
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Simple typing effect for terminal content
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    function typeText(elementId, text, speed = 70) {
      const element = document.getElementById(elementId);
      if (!element) return;
      
      element.textContent = '';
      let i = 0;
      
      function type() {
        if (i < text.length) {
          element.textContent += text.charAt(i);
          i++;
          setTimeout(type, speed);
        }
      }
      
      setTimeout(type, 500);
    }
    
    // Start typing effects with delays
    setTimeout(() => typeText('name-typing', 'Ignacio Castillo'), 500);
    setTimeout(() => typeText('role-typing', 'Desarrollador back-end y front-end'), 1500);
    setTimeout(() => typeText('status-typing', 'aprendiendo'), 3000);
    setTimeout(() => typeText('location-typing', 'Concepción, Chile'), 4000);
  });
</script>